snippet: A raft carrying Cuban migrants broke apart a few miles from Miami, leaving survivors clinging to debris for hours in the night. Ten were rescued or managed to swim to shore while three remained missing Monday afternoon....

headline.print_headline: 10 Cuban Migrants Found Near Miami, 3 Missing
headline.main: 10 Cuban Migrants Found Near Miami, 3 Missing

lead_paragraph: A raft carrying Cuban migrants broke apart a few miles from Miami, leaving survivors clinging to debris for hours in the night. Ten were rescued or managed to swim to shore while three remained missing Monday afternoon.
